Class Spatial_SBML

java.lang.Object
jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.Spatial_SBML
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
Spatial_Img_SBML, Spatial_Model_Edit, Spatial_Model_Validator, Spatial_Parametric_SBML
public abstract class Spatial_SBML
extends java.lang.Object
implements ij.plugin.PlugIn
The base class of this plugin (XitoSBML). It inherits from the ImageJ Plugin class. This class has run method which will be able to launch from * 'Plugins' -> 'XitoSBML'. The methods implemented by this plugin are described in src/main/resources/plugins.config. Date Created: Jun 17, 2015
Author:
Kaito Ii <ii@fun.bio.keio.ac.jp>, Akira Funahashi <funa@bio.keio.ac.jp>
